-- Allows operation of cathedral cross signs and visiblity of Baewynn after quest completion, until player leaves game
Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idSelf, "QST_Scos_Legacies_RecentlyComplete")

unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	local idSeerFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Scos_LochRaeth_Druid_Anthropomancer_Follower")
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSeerFollower) then
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONV_SEER_COMMENT01, idSelf, idSeerFollower)
	end

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	local idSeerFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Scos_LochRaeth_Druid_Anthropomancer_Follower")
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSeerFollower) then
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONV_SEER_COMMENT02, idSelf, idSeerFollower)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	local idSeerFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Scos_LochRaeth_Druid_Anthropomancer_Follower")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSeerFollower) then
	
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idSeerFollower)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idSeerFollower, false)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idSeerFollower, ID_DRUID_WARDSTONES, "NPC_RUN", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idSeerFollower, ID_DRUID_WARDSTONES)
		Hydra.QActorDelete(idSeerFollower)
		
	end
end
